# ZYNQ Peer

ZYNQ Peer is a WebRTC-based communication layer using PeerJS.

Supports:

- 📩 Messaging
- 🎥 Audio/video streaming
- 🔁 Auto-reconnect

---

## Quick Example

```js
const peer = ZYNQ.peer.get('remote-id');

peer.on('open', () => {
  peer.send('Hello');
});

peer.on('data', console.log);

peer.connect();
```
